8e2674f4b9b6c209ec818dbc7f33c32e6","tid":9383,"uid":43392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59257d63a8413feca7a3eeee83c8ec0ab232283","tid":9383,"uid":43392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"btw樓主有冇去熊本<br />\n唔知果邊依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee851e9286a5c139fa4925ab9aafd212a3c5ae5","tid":9383,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw樓主有冇去熊本<br />\n唔知果邊依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去完返黎 <br />\n市面冇乜野 但熊本城剩係可以行外圍"},{"pid":"8f9f1ec6d9adbca0847dabcf6fc7a4db00bcfe2c","tid":9383,"uid":43392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw樓主有冇去熊本<br />\n唔知果邊依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去完返黎 <br />\n市面冇乜野 但熊本城剩係可以行外圍</blockquote><br />\n其實我都預左熊本城入唔到<br />\n主要我自駕要去附近高千穗白川阿蘇<br />\n所以要住兩晚熊本 都未必會行到街<br />\n其實阿蘇都預左上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f221bff6e47be3148d4487a62cdc8b9241e5e7","tid":9383,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btw樓主有冇去熊本<br />\n唔知果邊依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去完返黎 <br />\n市面冇乜野 但熊本城剩係可以行外圍</blockquote><br />\n其實我都預左熊本城入唔到<br />\n主要我自駕要去附近高千穗白川阿蘇<br />\n所以要住兩晚熊本 都未必會行到街<br />\n其實阿蘇都預左上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高千穗有d路都封左<br />\n但好靚 e+去有紅葉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98cf6d5b0e4b7f8022d63b85701db3745ca8e18","tid":9383,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:35:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5d53f3ab9fe0a68e9a02ca1abed65c905aa920b4","tid":9383,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"岩岩番到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面提到熊本，高千穗同宮崎都有去<br />\n包容我慢慢更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1558378874a4725cb773ca3c22b4c31f1cee688","tid":9383,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:02:32.000Z","msg":"繼續鹿兒島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個九州真係無咩夜生活，太多數鋪頭收8點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實在唔係好慣<br />\n而收得最夜就係機鋪，收11-12點到，所以夜晚無野做就去玩下，700yen夾到隻卡比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/220151_f99d8b9f7cfde652596ef3bbbc7245d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F220151_f99d8b9f7cfde652596ef3bbbc7245d0.jpg&h=b20f0be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次買左全九州5日JR pass, 所以係到著後個日即刻去鹿兒島中央book定指定席，好好彩book到晒指宿玉手箱號同堆由布院之森<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抖左一晚之後就去指宿喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/215404_fd031d0055a57e3997b9556f97b761f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F215404_fd031d0055a57e3997b9556f97b761f9.jpg&h=f8538c48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6318a185b3fdc930df3133c4d8d133316240345","tid":9383,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩番到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面提到熊本，高千穗同宮崎都有去<br />\n包容我慢慢更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返黎行李等勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04fb82bcbb83fb50c76e617353b300d9771bc43","tid":9383,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩番到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面提到熊本，高千穗同宮崎都有去<br />\n包容我慢慢更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返黎行李等勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係等左幾耐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe04893c38289f41f99f2e3133aaa91e9ee7c05","tid":9383,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"指宿好細，大部分人去呢度係為左試下黑砂浴<br />\n<br />\n成個人堆係黑砂入面焗個十分鐘<br />\n唔會太熱，暖暖地會焗到一身汗，再浸過溫泉，身心舒暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/213303_bad5df7ff3a0c34ea9c022f9103032ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F213303_bad5df7ff3a0c34ea9c022f9103032ad.jpg&h=0109f0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/213504_3ef0eb3af5f174318faadc2761fbe4e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F213504_3ef0eb3af5f174318faadc2761fbe4e5.jpg&h=93c945aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/213505_3ef0eb3af5f174318faadc2761fbe4e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F213505_3ef0eb3af5f174318faadc2761fbe4e5.jpg&h=7bded50b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/213606_551f6b207c6a0140835322d01bad7da4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F213606_551f6b207c6a0140835322d01bad7da4.jpg&h=0274a505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c962d060704965bbdf003c80cb0b31311224f7","tid":9383,"uid":32614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"下年3月會去鹿兒島宮崎熊本<br />\n都係指宿櫻島日南呢d大路嘢，熊本為咗勝烈亭會再去一次，可能搭埋水前寺<br />\n不過暫時睇宮崎市好似幾悶下，會住一晚"},{"pid":"26a35d6264dc50855485c5627c0b4f9527016fa4","tid":9383,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:27:56.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗影到咁靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉鳴先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da74a5c4e89c4d1a3605631585e3d7c51401045","tid":9383,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下年3月會去鹿兒島宮崎熊本<br />\n都係指宿櫻島日南呢d大路嘢，熊本為咗勝烈亭會再去一次，可能搭埋水前寺<br />\n不過暫時睇宮崎市好似幾悶下，會住一晚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宮崎市冇野睇...<br />\n用黎做駁腳去日南/高千穗"},{"pid":"9afb980e18fad33f50d152824701a1fb494df028","tid":9383,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:31:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1759344f364e360e23ae940d75d7be5a505f5e1d","tid":9383,"uid":14474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:49:23.000Z","msg":"熊本/博多有冇咩餐廳推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6815b4b74dbaf4ab0bdedb12120826000d32e3","tid":9383,"uid":35610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熊本/博多有冇咩餐廳推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu